<div id="industries-of-homeworkers" class="section__content--markdown">
<section>
<header>
<h2><span class="section__content-number">3.</span> Industries of homeworkers</h2>
</header>
<p>The extent to which people can and do work from home varies by industrial sector.</p><p>
<div class="markdown-chart-container panel--bottom-mar print--avoid-break">
